<p t="5689" d="3404" wp="2" ws="1"><s p="2">​</s><s>​</s><s p="3">​ ​Nanase-chan! I&#39;d like to!​ ​</s><s p="2">​
​</s><s p="3">​ ​Ask a question!​ ​</s><s p="2">​</s></p>
<p t="9093" d="2469" wp="2" ws="1"><s p="2">​</s><s>​</s><s p="4">​ ​Honoka-san?​ ​</s><s p="2">​
​</s><s p="4">​ ​What seems to be the matter?​ ​</s><s p="2">​</s></p>
<p t="11562" d="3703" wp="2" ws="1"><s p="2">​</s><s>​</s><s p="3">​ ​So umm, I&#39;d like to ask​ ​</s><s p="2">​
​</s><s p="3">​ ​some stuff about this school.​ ​</s><s p="2">​</s></p>
<p t="15265" d="3471" wp="2" ws="1"><s p="2">​</s><s>​</s><s p="3">​ ​Your family established​ ​</s><s p="2">​
​</s><s p="3">​ ​this school, right?​ ​</s><s p="2">​</s></p>
<p t="18736" d="1701" wp="2" ws="1"><s p="2">​</s><s>​</s><s p="4">​ ​Why yes, that is correct...​ ​</s><s p="2">​</s></p>
<p t="20437" d="1068" wp="2" ws="1"><s p="2">​</s><s>​</s><s p="4">​ ​What about it?​ ​</s><s p="2">​</s></p>
<p t="21505" d="2002" wp="2" ws="1"><s p="2">​</s><s>​</s><s p="3">​ ​Does the land around here​ ​</s><s p="2">​
​</s><s p="3">​ ​have any &quot;history&quot; to it​ ​</s><s p="2">​</s></p>
<p t="23507" d="2002" wp="2" ws="1"><s p="2">​</s><s>​</s><s p="3">​ ​before the school was put up?​ ​</s><s p="2">​</s></p>
<p t="25509" d="1268" wp="2" ws="1"><s p="2">​</s><s>​</s><s p="3">​ ​Like, was it a burial ground?​ ​</s><s p="2">​</s></p>
<p t="26777" d="2369" wp="2" ws="1"><s p="2">​</s><s>​</s><s p="3">​ ​Or did someone​ ​</s><s p="2">​
​</s><s p="3">​ ​die here or anything?​ ​</s><s p="2">​</s></p>
<p t="29146" d="2803" wp="2" ws="1"><s p="2">​</s><s>​</s><s p="4">​ ​I do not know where​ ​</s><s p="2">​
​</s><s p="4">​ ​you picked up such rumors,​ ​</s><s p="2">​</s></p>
<p t="31949" d="2436" wp="2" ws="1"><s p="2">​</s><s>​</s><s p="4">​ ​but absolutely none of them​ ​</s><s p="2">​
​</s><s p="4">​ ​are true.​ ​</s><s p="2">​</s></p>
<p t="34385" d="2702" wp="2" ws="1"><s p="2">​</s><s>​</s><s p="4">​ ​All the necessary cleansing​ ​</s><s p="2">​
​</s><s p="4">​ ​rites were performed​ ​</s><s p="2">​</s></p>
<p t="37087" d="2503" wp="2" ws="1"><s p="2">​</s><s>​</s><s p="4">​ ​prior to the construction​ ​</s><s p="2">​
​</s><s p="4">​ ​of the school building.​ ​</s><s p="2">​</s></p>
<p t="39590" d="2135" wp="2" ws="1"><s p="2">​</s><s>​</s><s p="4">​ ​This school is not tainted.​ ​</s><s p="2">​</s></p>
<p t="41725" d="1402" wp="2" ws="1"><s p="2">​</s><s>​</s><s p="3">​ ​Is that so...​ ​</s><s p="2">​</s></p>
<p t="43127" d="3770" wp="2" ws="1"><s p="2">​</s><s>​</s><s p="3">​ ​Maybe that other rumor​ ​</s><s p="2">​
​</s><s p="3">​ ​is true, though.​ ​</s><s p="2">​</s></p>
<p t="46897" d="1668" wp="2" ws="1"><s p="2">​</s><s>​</s><s p="4">​ ​I do not follow.​ ​</s><s p="2">​
​</s><s p="4">​ ​What are you talking about?​ ​</s><s p="2">​</s></p>
<p t="48565" d="468" wp="2" ws="1"><s p="2">​</s><s>​</s><s p="3">​ ​Uh...​ ​</s><s p="2">​</s></p>
<p t="49033" d="3136" wp="2" ws="1"><s p="2">​</s><s>​</s><s p="3">​ ​Rumor has it there&#39;s a ghost​ ​</s><s p="2">​
​</s><s p="3">​ ​in the Art Prep Room!​ ​</s><s p="2">​</s></p>
<p t="52169" d="3036" wp="2" ws="1"><s p="2">​</s><s>​</s><s p="3">​ ​I wanna see if it&#39;s true,​ ​</s><s p="2">​
​</s><s p="3">​ ​so I&#39;m gathering information!​ ​</s><s p="2">​</s></p>
<p t="55205" d="1135" wp="2" ws="1"><s p="2">​</s><s>​</s><s p="4">​ ​Sigh...​ ​</s><s p="2">​</s></p>
<p t="56340" d="3737" wp="2" ws="1"><s p="2">​</s><s>​</s><s p="4">​ ​Nothing good will​ ​</s><s p="2">​
​</s><s p="4">​ ​come about chasing rumors.​ ​</s><s p="2">​</s></p>
<p t="60077" d="2369" wp="2" ws="1"><s p="2">​</s><s>​</s><s p="3">​ ​Sakura-chan was the one who​ ​</s><s p="2">​
​</s><s p="3">​ ​told me about this, though.​ ​</s><s p="2">​</s></p>
<p t="62446" d="1101" wp="2" ws="1"><s p="2">​</s><s>​</s><s p="4">​ ​You heard it from her?​ ​</s><s p="2">​</s></p>
<p t="63547" d="634" wp="2" ws="1"><s p="2">​</s><s>​</s><s p="3">​ ​Yeah!​ ​</s><s p="2">​</s></p>
<p t="64181" d="2936" wp="2" ws="1"><s p="2">​</s><s>​</s><s p="3">​ ​She&#39;s a shrine maiden,​ ​</s><s p="2">​
​</s><s p="3">​ ​so it sounds plausible, right?​ ​</s><s p="2">​</s></p>
<p t="67117" d="2670" wp="2" ws="1"><s p="2">​</s><s>​</s><s p="3">​ ​I think it&#39;s worth looking into.​ ​</s><s p="2">​</s></p>
<p t="69787" d="1935" wp="2" ws="1"><s p="2">​</s><s>​</s><s p="4">​ ​That will not be necessary.​ ​</s><s p="2">​</s></p>
<p t="71722" d="2135" wp="2" ws="1"><s p="2">​</s><s>​</s><s p="4">​ ​Whatever Sakura-san said​ ​</s><s p="2">​
​</s><s p="4">​ ​is nonsense.​ ​</s><s p="2">​</s></p>
<p t="73857" d="601" wp="2" ws="1"><s p="2">​</s><s>​</s><s p="3">​ ​Huh?​ ​</s><s p="2">​</s></p>
<p t="74458" d="2769" wp="2" ws="1"><s p="2">​</s><s>​</s><s p="4">​ ​Father and Grandfather​ ​</s><s p="2">​
​</s><s p="4">​ ​built this school.​ ​</s><s p="2">​</s></p>
<p t="77227" d="2336" wp="2" ws="1"><s p="2">​</s><s>​</s><s p="4">​ ​It could not possibly be tainted.​ ​</s><s p="2">​</s></p>
<p t="80831" d="2970" wp="2" ws="1"><s p="2">​</s><s>​</s><s p="3">​ ​Wanna see for yourself, then?​ ​</s><s p="2">​</s></p>
<p t="83801" d="1835" wp="2" ws="1"><s p="2">​</s><s>​</s><s p="4">​ ​Very well.​ ​</s><s p="2">​</s></p>
<p t="85636" d="2102" wp="2" ws="1"><s p="2">​</s><s>​</s><s p="4">​ ​The Art Prep Room, yes?​ ​</s><s p="2">​
​</s><s p="4">​ ​I will go there now—​ ​</s><s p="2">​</s></p>
<p t="87738" d="2669" wp="2" ws="1"><s p="2">​</s><s>​</s><s p="3">​ ​Oh, no point in​ ​</s><s p="2">​
​</s><s p="3">​ ​checking it out now.​ ​</s><s p="2">​</s></p>
<p t="90407" d="2836" wp="2" ws="1"><s p="2">​</s><s>​</s><s p="3">​ ​They say it only​ ​</s><s p="2">​
​</s><s p="3">​ ​comes out at night!​ ​</s><s p="2">​</s></p>
<p t="93243" d="1902" wp="2" ws="1"><s p="2">​</s><s>​</s><s p="4">​ ​Wait, you mean to tell me...​ ​</s><s p="2">​</s></p>
<p t="95145" d="2069" wp="2" ws="1"><s p="2">​</s><s>​</s><s p="3">​ ​Yep, it&#39;s a test of courage!​ ​</s><s p="2">​</s></p>
<p t="97214" d="2970" wp="2" ws="1"><s p="2">​</s><s>​</s><s p="3">​ ​I&#39;ll let you know when it&#39;s​ ​</s><s p="2">​
​</s><s p="3">​ ​happening, so don&#39;t chicken out!​ ​</s><s p="2">​</s></p>
</body>
